<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="be-better-off-doing-sth">(be) better off doing sth</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>最好做某事：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— We are planning to go to London by train. 
我们计划乘火车去伦敦。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— I think you would be better off taking the plane. 
我觉得你们乘飞机比较好。</p></div></div>